00:04:07.447 --> 00:04:08.683 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:04:09.917 --> 00:04:10.852 position:27% line:89% align:start
Tell me, Akagami.

00:04:10.985 --> 00:04:12.787 position:21% line:83% align:start
