as far as you're concerned,

00:04:27.935 --> 00:04:30.138 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm apparently nothing more
than a big pair of tits.

00:04:30.270 --> 00:04:31.672 position:44% line:89% align:start
Eep!

00:04:31.806 --> 00:04:33.174 position:13% line:83% align:start
[KIKI] "Point at the moon,
and you see a finger."

00:04:33.306 --> 00:04:34.776 position:30% line:83% align:start
In other words,
people's attention

00:04:34.909 --> 00:04:37.277 position:27% line:83% align:start
tends to be drawn
to the extended finger itself

00:04:37.410 --> 00:04:39.412 position:21% line:83% align:start
rather than the moon
it's directed at.

00:04:39.614 --> 00:04:42.282 position:16% line:83% align:start
Likewise, when I pointed
at my breasts,

00:04:42.482 --> 00:04:44.152 position:10% line:89% align:start
I knew it would distract you.

00:04:44.384 --> 00:04:45.887 position:24% line:89% align:start
Hey, you set me up!

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:48.421 position:7% line:83% align:start
[KIKI] You can't allow yourself
to lose sight of what matters.

00:04:48.556 --> 00:04:52.560 position:7% line:83% align:start
A finger is a prominent signal,
but if you never look past it,

00:04:52.693 --> 00:04:54.028 position:21% line:89% align:start
your gaze won't reach

00:04:54.162 --> 00:04:56.296 position:10% line:83% align:start
the moon you should be paying
attention to.

00:04:56.429 --> 00:04:58.633 position:33% line:83% align:start
Interesting.
But what does it mean?

00:04:58.766 --> 00:05:01.035 position:19% line:83% align:start
