Yuzuki to me?

00:05:01.202 --> 00:05:02.603 position:16% line:89% align:start
Tell me how you see her.

00:05:04.205 --> 00:05:05.438 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AKAGAMI]
Yuzuki, huh?

00:05:06.174 --> 00:05:07.241 position:27% line:89% align:start
She's dependable.

00:05:07.642 --> 00:05:10.211 position:7% line:83% align:start
A bit careless at times, maybe.
But still..

00:05:10.845 --> 00:05:13.014 position:27% line:83% align:start
she's so positive
and well-adjusted.

00:05:15.216 --> 00:05:17.919 position:19% line:83% align:start
She's certainly a much
stronger person than I am.

00:05:18.786 --> 00:05:21.889 position:19% line:83% align:start
