a closer look, Akagami.

00:05:22.355 --> 00:05:23.323 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:05:23.456 --> 00:05:24.292 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Hey, Kiki.
-[purring]

00:05:24.424 --> 00:05:25.425 position:21% line:89% align:start
